The '''Bureau of Patriotic Defense''' was formed on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Troxar]] during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], and was officially neutral. However, its members were loyal to the [[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|Separatists]], and planned to feign surrendering to the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Republic]] in order to allow Separatist forces to move in and take the planet after [[Clone trooper/Legends|clone trooper]] forces had pulled out. [[Palpatine/Legends|Darth Sidious]] instructed [[Count/Legends|Count]] [[Dooku/Legends|Dooku]] to forestall this action, using Troxar as a battleground where Republic forces continued to be killed for no apparent reason.

